These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
City: colone, rome, nizza
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, hip-hop, folk
1. the person traveling to colone is in an even position##4
2. the fan of electronic is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
3. the fan of electronic is the person traveling to rome##1
4. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| City   | nizza | colone | rome |
| Music-Genre    | hip-hop    | folk | electronic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, blend, chaman
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, soccer, skateboarding
1. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Cigar       | blend | chaman | swisher |
| Sport   | skateboarding    | soccer     | ice-hockey        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, november, january
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, black, coral
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Birthday         | january     | november | august |
| Color   | black | purple     | coral  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, dog, goldfish
There 3 different types of food: mango, banana, apple
1. the owner of the dog is the person eating banana##1
2. the owner of the lizard is the person eating apple##1
3. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Pet   | goldfish | dog  | lizard  |
| Food         | mango  | banana | apple |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
3 different games are played: go, snooker, billiard
City: paris, london, colone
1. the person playing billiard is between the person playing go and the person traveling to paris##2
2. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Game         | go   | billiard | snooker    |
| City   | london | colone     | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, 7up
The people have 3 different jobs:  electrician, fisherman, nurse
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the fisherman##1
2. the nurse is the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage   | coffee | 7up | iced-tea   |
| Job   | nurse     | electrician    | fisherman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, azalea
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, havana, dannemann
1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsorchid is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who growsazalea##2
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
4. the game-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Flower   | azalea | orchid | iris |
| Cigar           | havana         | game         | dannemann |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, chestnut, red
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, camping, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who likes purple##2
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Color   | chestnut | red | purple |
| Hobby    | camping    | magic-tricks | woodworking     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, lemonade
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, magic-tricks, collecting
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | soy-milk  | tea  |
| Hobby         | collecting | magic-tricks | drawing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
