3 different pets are kept: cat, horse, dog
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
2. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Color   | blood-red    | pink      | aquamarine |
| Pet       | horse | dog | cat   |

