.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, filmmaking, collecting
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, amaryllis, poppy
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who growspoppy is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | collecting | fishing |
| Flower   | amaryllis | poppy   | sunflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
House: cottage, modern, futuristic
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, scientist, project-manager
1. the project-manager is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the cottage house is the project-manager##1
3. the scientist is on the left or right of the modern house##3
4. the project-manager is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| House   | futuristic | modern | cottage |
| Job     | scientist     | lawyer   | project-manager        |

