.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, superhero, adventure
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, sprite, coffee
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person drinking water is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | western | superhero   |
| Beverage         | sprite | coffee   | water |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend, bluemaster
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
1. the bluemaster-smoker is between the blend-smoker and the person drinking iced-tea##2
2. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Cigar   | blend | bluemaster | bongani |
| Beverage     | 7up    | hot-chocolate  | iced-tea   |

