.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, backgammon
There are 3 different favourite colors: brown, coral, white
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
4. the person playing backgammon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Game   | snooker  | backgammon     | mah-jongg |
| Color   | coral | brown | white    |

