.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, american, russian
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, snowmobile, bike
1. the person driving the bike is the russian##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the japanese##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Nationality          | russian | japanese | american  |
| Transport   | bike      | quad-bike  | snowmobile |

