.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, february, december
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, orange, white
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Birthday   | january | december | february    |
| Color           | orange     | white  | apricot |

