.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, baseball, snowboarding
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, vegafina, swisher
1. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Sport         | snowboarding | parkour   | baseball |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | aristoff | swisher      |

