.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, february, september
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, van, car
1. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
2. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Birthday      | april | february | september |
| Transport   | van   | car          | quad-bike |

