.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, funk, salsa
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, chess, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of salsa is in an even position##4
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre     | funk  | salsa   | soul |
| Hobby   | fishing | chess | collecting       |

 